      <span class="font-rye text-2xl font-bold">Cuba Tattoo Studio</span>
      <span class="text-gray-400">Calle 23 #123, La Habana, Cuba</span>
      <span class="text-gray-400">+53 5555 5555</span>
      <span class="text-gray-400">info@cubatattoostudio.com</span>
    </div>
